title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life
itunes:title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life
description:
I want to encourage you today that God has great purpose for your life. You hold meaning, you hold potential, you hold everything you need to make this earth a better place. I want to charge us today to just reevaluate our life and realize we are here for God's purpose and God's glory. Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
